<p data-index="5765">Compute the net cash provided (used) by investing activities.</p>
<p id="BE5.15_1" data-index="5766"><b data-index="5767"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="5768">BE5.15</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="5769"><b data-index="5770">(LO <a href="#h3_0003" data-index="5771" data-section-index="15" data-section-idref="h3_0003" data-target-data-index="2153">3</a>)</b></span> Use the information presented in <a href="#BE5.14_1" data-index="5772" data-section-index="15" data-section-idref="BE5.14_1" data-target-data-index="5728">BE5.14</a> for Martinez Corporation to compute the net cash used (provided) by financing activities.</p>
