<h4 data-index="6885"><span class="red" data-index="6886">Instructions</span></h4>
<p data-index="6887">Prepare a balance sheet at December 31, 2020, for Scott Butler Corporation. (Ignore income taxes.)</p>
<p id="E5.13_1" data-index="6888"><b data-index="6889"><span class="codeColorBlue2" data-index="6890">E5.13</span></b> <span class="red" data-index="6891"><b data-index="6892">(LO <a href="#h3_0003" data-index="6893" data-section-index="15" data-section-idref="h3_0003" data-target-data-index="2153">3</a>)</b></span> <span class="bold" data-index="6894">(Statement of Cash Flows—Classifications)</span> The major classifications of activities reported in the statement of cash flows are operating, investing, and financing. Classify each of the transactions listed below as:</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6895"><span class="label" data-index="6896"><b data-index="6897">1.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Operating activity—add to net income.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6898"><span class="label" data-index="6899"><b data-index="6900">2.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Operating activity—deduct from net income.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6901"><span class="label" data-index="6902"><b data-index="6903">3.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Investing activity.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6904"><span class="label" data-index="6905"><b data-index="6906">4.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Financing activity.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6907"><span class="label" data-index="6908"><b data-index="6909">5.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Reported as significant noncash activity.</p>
<p data-index="6910">The transactions are as follows.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6911"><span class="label" data-index="6912"><b data-index="6913">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Issuance of common stock.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6914"><span class="label" data-index="6915"><b data-index="6916">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Purchase of land and building.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6917"><span class="label" data-index="6918"><b data-index="6919">c.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Redemption of bonds.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6920"><span class="label" data-index="6921"><b data-index="6922">d.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Sale of equipment.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6923"><span class="label" data-index="6924"><b data-index="6925">e.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Depreciation of machinery.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6926"><span class="label" data-index="6927"><b data-index="6928">f.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Amortization of patent.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6929"><span class="label" data-index="6930"><b data-index="6931">g.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Issuance of bonds for plant assets.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="6932"><span class="label" data-index="6933"><b data-index="6934">h.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Payment of cash dividends.</p>
