<h4 data-index="8944"><span class="red" data-index="8945">Instructions</span></h4>
<p class="latin1" data-index="8946"><span class="label" data-index="8947"><b data-index="8948">a.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> Organize the accounts in the general order in which they would have been presented in a classified balance sheet.</p>
<p class="latin1" data-index="8949"><span class="label" data-index="8950"><b data-index="8951">b.</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> When several of the branch locations of the Automotive Division were closed, what balance sheet accounts were most likely affected? Did the balance in those accounts decrease or increase?</p>
</section>
